<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Add New Session</title>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <a href="/sessions">Community Activity</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <h1>Add New Session</h1>
    <div id="add-session-info">
        <p>Did you just have a climbing session that you just Need to brag about? 
            Log it below! Share your name, the grade that you attempted and whether or not you 
            sent (climber speak for completed) it! After you're done sharing your send, take a look 
            at what other climbers have sent for inspiration for your next session. 
        </p>
    </div>
    <form action="/sessions" method="post">
        <label for="name">Name: </label>
        <input type="text" name="name" id="name">
        <label for="boulderGrade">Boulder Grade: </label>
        <select id="boulder-grade" name="boulderGrade">
            <option value="vb">VB</option>
            <option value="vb">V0</option>
            <option value="v1">V1</option>
            <option value="v2">V2</option>
            <option value="v3">V3</option>
            <option value="v4">V4</option>
            <option value="v5">V5</option>
            <option value="v6">V6</option>
            <option value="v7">V7</option>
            <option value="v8">V8</option>
            <option value="v9">V9</option>
            <option value="v10">V10</option>
            <option value="v11">V11</option>
            <option value="v12">V12</option>
        </select>
        <label for="isSent">Did you send it!?</label>
        <select id="is-sent" name="isSent">
            <option value="yes">Heck yeah!</option>
            <option value="no">Not yet ðŸ’ª</option>
        </select>
        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
</body>
</html>